WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
KingVan Technology presents our high-performance laser marking machine,

00:00:05.500 --> 00:00:10.000
specially designed for thermal break strips used in aluminum windows and doors.

00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:16.000
Compared with manual marking, our machine is much faster

00:00:16.500 --> 00:00:20.000
and requires only one person to operate,

00:00:20.500 --> 00:00:25.000
effectively saving labor costs

00:00:25.500 --> 00:00:29.000
while greatly improving overall working efficiency.

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:35.000
It supports double-sided marking on both front and back surfaces,

00:00:35.500 --> 00:00:40.000
with a maximum processing capacity of up to 1 ton of thermal strips per hour.

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:45.000
The marking effect is clear, beautiful, and highly precise.

00:00:46.000 --> 00:00:49.000
What's more, laser marking requires no consumables at all,

00:00:49.500 --> 00:00:53.000
greatly reducing your long-term operating expenses.

00:00:54.000 --> 00:00:58.000
And we back every machine with a lifetime warranty,

00:00:58.500 --> 00:01:02.000
giving you complete peace of mind.

00:01:03.000 --> 00:01:08.000
Choose KingVan for a smarter, more efficient, and more reliable thermal strip marking solution.
